{"tid":741311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「刺客」首在港島犯案，新巴座椅頭枕插兩針","createTime":"2018-07-13T14:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T14:32:10.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"08e17c7d8e60feb6065a2379bbffe2d9e1fc1759","tid":741311,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T14:20:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180713/photo/bkn-20180713192256565-0713_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180713221144\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180713%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180713192256565-0713_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180713221144&h=f7cd737e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「刺客」首次在新巴犯案，座椅被插上兩支大頭針<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n巴士放針事件沒完沒了，今午(13日)九巴905號線被放針，有男乘客遭拮傷後，「刺客」竟首次在港島的新巴犯案，晚上7時許，一輛14號線新巴，抵達西灣河太康街38號嘉亨灣巴士總站時，姓楊(33歲)男車長接獲乘客通知，指於上層近尾排近窗口的座椅頭枕邊位置，發現插有2支長約6厘米大頭針。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180713/photo/bkn-20180713192256565-0713_00822_001_02b.jpg?20180713221144\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180713%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180713192256565-0713_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20180713221144&h=43378ff3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n事件中幸無乘客受傷，楊其後通知站長並報警求助。警員接報到場，經初步調查後，案件列作刑事毀壞，交由東區警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。新巴發言人表示，涉事巴士裝有閉路電視，公司會配合警方調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180713/photo/bkn-20180713192256565-0713_00822_001_04b.jpg?20180713221144\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180713%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180713192256565-0713_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20180713221144&h=f30adda3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180713/bkn-20180713192256565-0713_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180713%2Fbkn-20180713192256565-0713_00822_001.html&d=ceD5UE%2FeaeY398%2BLRcCkacmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=af5b5a1f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180713/bkn-20180713192256565-0713_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"cff09a87deea2010120817b17d3dab1eed6b75df","tid":741311,"uid":58491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T14:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母 咁撚毒"},{"pid":"23e4a1b275b2d47c56f7b253ca0468b54465dfb4","tid":741311,"uid":125731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cff09a87deea2010120817b17d3dab1eed6b75df","tid":741311,"uid":58491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T14:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母 咁撚毒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T14:30:25.000Z","msg":"唔係針口向出 , 會桔到人咩 ??"},{"pid":"61b7479a9c55df7d7324af5ce7613590bc4445f1","tid":741311,"uid":58491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23e4a1b275b2d47c56f7b253ca0468b54465dfb4","tid":741311,"uid":125731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cff09a87deea2010120817b17d3dab1eed6b75df","tid":741311,"uid":58491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T14:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母 咁撚毒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T14:30:25.000Z","msg":"唔係針口向出 , 會桔到人咩 ??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T14:32:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自膠"}]}